<br>
btw you kill doomfires in 2 min 30 sec. 45k hp mobs? thats a nice 1200dps, and 1600*4/4.95 = 1293 meaning a crit every hit for 28 repetitions at .18^29...<br>
2.52 x 10^-20 % (yes that number has 20 zeros in front of it). relying on luck overmuch?..<br>
<br>
when it comes down to it, whether or not to use atol's or bof depends on whether or not you have the pwndagger. additionally. why is this even significant when after 170AAs, the remaining ones are very very marginal in use? yes, I can get lightning reflexes 2-3% faster, yow! in my experience it has been little under 3 casts to get 4 doomfire doods all snared up, marking this down for 10aas there when i was making quadstats. otu of a 45k hp mob, this translates to 1-2% more xp.<br>
<br>
some minor quad stats, both 1800+ casts:<br>
Atol Fizzle %: 1.56<br>
Pillar of Frost Fizzle %: 1.47<br>
<br>
The above illustrates the difference of the +25 resist mod to atol's. also consider that I have a specialization to evocation, so that this fizzle reduction chance for the 2 level 51 spells is somewhere under a tenth of a percent. I would say it doesn't even do anything, like brilliance of ro is believed to, given the closeness of these stats.<br>
<br>
I concede to Elyia that indeed, bof is superior to me, having calcualted myself that it owuld lend me on average +1.26% to my aaxp rate. If I put this good point to use, perhaps doing 200% aaxp/hour I shall get an extra 3% aaxp per hour... a very significant total I think, that shall give me another AA when I have 300 aa total, and another aa when I have 400 aa total. <br>
<br>
in a very long time from now, I will have put this knowledge to good use to get another AA for strong root!<br>
<br>
bottom line is that its effectively negligable given that personally I have added up 10 aaxp of quads and found ~2.5 recasts on doomfires used. 1.26% more <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :x --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/sick.gif ALT=":x"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26600.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=26600.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=26600.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26600.topic&index=22><img src=http://www.graffe.com/images/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=26600.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=26600.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26600.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies" align=absmiddle> Click to receive email notification of replies</a><br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topic